      "system": {
        "description": {
          "value": "<p><strong>Trigger</strong> A living creature remains in area C7 for more than 1 round.</p>\n<p><strong>Effect</strong> A ghostly guard attempts to enter the body of a random living creature in the room. The target must attempt a @Check[type:will|dc:30] save or become @Compendium[pf2e.conditionitems.Confused]{Confused} for 1 minute. The haunt then rolls initiative.</p>"
